'''Larry Wall''' is the developer of the [[Perl]] programming language.  Wall is also known as the original author of the [[rn]] [[Usenet]] software, and the nearly universally used [[patch]]. He has won the [[IOCCC]] twice.

See also:
[[Famous programmer]]

